  "remarks": "\n Joint Stock Company Salavat Chemical Plant (hereafter JSC SALAVAT CHEMICAL PLANT), a subsidiary of Russian State space agency Roscosmos. JSC SALAVAT CHEMICAL PLANT has been and is been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting by carrying on business in the Russia chemicals sector a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
